{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:23:21.841Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude Cookbook and AWS Prescriptive Guidance for agentic AI patterns, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Prompt Chaining\""},{"type":"text","text":" is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"multi-LLM workflow pattern that decomposes complex tasks into sequential subtasks"},{"type":"text","text":", where each step builds on previous results."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt chaining breaks a complex task into a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"sequence of discrete LLM invocations"},{"type":"text","text":", where each step processes or builds upon the output of the previous one. Instead of one massive prompt, you create a chain of smaller, focused prompts."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Basic Flow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: Prompt → Output A\nStep 2: Prompt + Output A → Output B\nStep 3: Prompt + Output B → Final Result"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each step is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"controlled, discrete LLM call"},{"type":"text","text":" that transforms the output toward the final desired state."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The workflow follows a linear chain pattern:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Phase"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"c