xt stage of reasoning"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade cost/latency for improved performance on complex tasks"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Enables structured thinking, progressive transformation, layered analysis"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Useful for: document review, code generation, knowledge extraction, content refinement"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Provides transparency, controllability, and reliability over single-shot prompts"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Can add external validation, filtering, or enrichment between steps"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Anthropic moved beyond manual prompt chaining"},{"type":"text","text":" to Dynamic Workflows (Claude writes harness code automatically)"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For production-scale agents, prefer Dynamic Workflows (fan-out/synthesize, loop-until-done, adversarial verification) over hand-chaining 50 prompts."}]}]}}
